{"tid":2284308,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"官質疑警毋須揮棍","createTime":"2020-11-13T08:01:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-13T08:34:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"784dd323f7884024f8edf8ce8eccee0a3ed73705","tid":2284308,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T08:01:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201113/6PSQ624TKFG2ZMRPIROMFL677I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201113%2F6PSQ624TKFG2ZMRPIROMFL677I%2F&d=28xXuG3%2BZgR4L17YEenOIg%2BoCD4UrwaevtQIqI6x5z0%3D&h=e814a606\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201113%2F6PSQ624TKFG2ZMRPIROMFL677I%2F&h=aa8ad385\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201113/6PSQ624TKFG2ZMRPIROMFL677I/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n官質疑警毋須揮棍<br />\n<br />\n【區議員阻差案】【本報訊】沙田區議員許銳宇去年7月14日在新城市廣場衝突中協助調停，卻被控阻差辦公罪，許不認罪昨受審。時發時身在現場的警長供稱，被告用身體阻礙他追捕疑犯，另有示威者向他施襲。惟署理主任裁判官溫紹明看過案發影片後指出，現場有其他警員揮動警棍，「其實你都唔知自己俾咩打中」，警長同意。溫官質疑：「要制服咪捉住佢囉，你哋都唔少人，應該唔使揮棍。」警長對此沒回應。<br />\n<br />\n被告許銳宇（32歲）否認當日故意阻撓警署警長葉克勤執行職務。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ejs3vpiQumDwUX2Y6of28zBx3JA=/588x331/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Y7K5QMFZP5HZLHMBKU76IZZ42Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fejs3vpiQumDwUX2Y6of28zBx3JA%3D%2F588x331%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FY7K5QMFZP5HZLHMBKU76IZZ42Q.jpg&h=3cfe5183&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n葉克勤<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n辯方：被告舉傘保護警員記者<br />\n<br />\n控方結案陳詞指，被告與其他示威者合力拉走疑犯，並用身體阻擋葉，行為形同「搶犯」。惟辯方指被告從沒拉開疑犯，疑犯是被大批示威者扯走；又指當晚被告不斷舉傘保護警員、記者等人，冀使衝突降溫。溫官亦指，影片清楚顯示被告嘗試阻止警員攻擊示威者。案件下月3日裁決。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：STCC3744/19"},{"pid":"8d5f85737d5b4560e2ff18bc0cd3e1fa3d32e015","tid":2284308,"uid":301050,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T08:13:10.000Z","msg":"黑警冇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地嘅職務就係打人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n溫官唔好亂講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80507b931232f7289f01f0e5a05edb1d8e966b43","tid":2284308,"uid":165749,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T08:31:39.000Z","msg":"賴控制唔到支棍亂咁郁羅，支棍明顯低EQ<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb27d62b66e2fd0e0efad57a278590e50af0f700","tid":2284308,"uid":32721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T08:34:01.000Z","msg":"你整花支警棍，告你刑事毀壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"396ef8994918945ccc20be3b987f5986ce0dfcdd","tid":2284308,"uid":82394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T08:34:12.000Z","msg":"清官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}